org.rapla.components.util.undo

Class CommandHistory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rapla.components.util.undo.CommandHistory

  • public class CommandHistory
extends Object
    This is where all the committed actions are saved. A list will be initialized, every action is an item of this list. There is a list for the calendar view, and one for the edit view.
    Author:
    Jens Fritz
